Sketches - Privacy
Privacy Policy for Sketches Mobile Application
This Privacy Policy describes how Sketches ("we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, and shares personal information when you use our mobile application, Sketches (the "App"). By using the App, you consent to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.
You can access to limited Sketches features or you can subscribe for unlimited access to all features.
